I didn’t find any discussion explaining why `pi` should prefer GitHub over aqua. The only relevant discussion was #10439, and the prior PR #9792 actually said aqua should be the default while merging GitHub first.

I made the fix and opened PR: [jdx/mise#10727](https://github.com/jdx/mise/pull/10727)

Validation passed:
- `cargo test registry::tests::test_registry_iteration_is_sorted`
- `cargo run --quiet -- registry pi` now prints aqua first

